## 3. Key Entities

### Tickets

Entities: `Tickets`, `TicketNotes`, `TicketCharges`, `TicketHistory`, `TicketSecondaryResources`, `TicketCategories`, `ServiceLevelAgreementResults`, `TicketChecklistItems`, `TicketAdditionalContacts`, `TicketAdditionalConfigurationItems`, `TicketTagAssociations`

**Ticket status values:**
| Value | Status |
|-------|--------|
| 1 | New |
| 2 | In Progress |
| 3 | Waiting Customer |
| 4 | Waiting Vendor |
| 5 | Complete |
| 6 | Cancelled |
| 7 | Resolved |

**Key fields:** `id`, `ticketNumber`, `title`, `status`, `priority`, `companyID`, `contactID`, `assignedResourceID`, `assignedResourceroleID`, `queueID`, `issueType`, `subIssueType`, `ticketType`, `source`, `billingCodeID`, `contractID`, `configurationItemID`, `projectID`, `dueDateTime`, `estimatedHours`, `description`, `resolution`, `createDate`, `completedDate`, `lastActivityDate`, `firstResponseDateTime`, `firstResponseDueDateTime`, `resolvedDateTime`, `resolvedDueDateTime`, `serviceLevelAgreementID`

Limits: max 50 secondary resources, 40 checklist items, 30 additional contacts, 100 additional assets, 30 tags per ticket.

### Companies

Entity: `Companies` (max 200 UDFs, cannot delete)

**CompanyType values:**
| Value | Type |
|-------|------|
| 1 | Customer |
| 2 | Lead |
| 3 | Prospect |
| 4 | Dead |
| 5 | Cancelation |
| 6 | Vendor |
| 7 | Partner |

**Key fields:** `id`, `companyName`, `companyType`, `companyCategoryID`, `ownerResourceID`, `phone`, `address1`, `address2`, `city`, `state`, `postalCode`, `countryID`, `isActive`, `parentCompanyID`, `webAddress`, `marketSegmentID`, `territoryID`, `classification`, `createDate`, `lastActivityDate`, `lastTrackedModifiedDateTime`, `currencyID`

### Contacts

Entity: `Contacts` (max 100 UDFs)

**Key fields:** `id`, `firstName`, `lastName`, `companyID`, `emailAddress`, `phone`, `isActive`, `primaryContact`, `title`, `createDate`, `lastModifiedDate`

Only one `primaryContact` per company. `companyID` is read-only after creation.

### Projects

Entity: `Projects` (max 200 UDFs)

**Key fields:** `id`, `projectName`, `companyID`, `projectType`, `status`, `startDateTime`, `endDateTime`, `estimatedHours` (read-only), `actualHours` (read-only), `estimatedSalesCost`, `laborEstimatedCosts`, `laborEstimatedRevenue`, `laborEstimatedMarginPercentage` (read-only), `projectLeadResourceID`, `contractID`, `description`, `completedPercentage` (read-only)

Baseline projects are read-only via API. Cannot update `startDateTime` if tasks exist.

### Tasks

Entity: `Tasks` (max 100 UDFs)

**Key fields:** `id`, `title`, `projectID`, `status`, `taskType`, `startDateTime`, `endDateTime`, `estimatedHours`, `assignedResourceID`, `assignedResourceroleID`, `billingCodeID`, `phaseID`, `priorityLabel`, `description`, `completedDateTime` (read-only), `remainingHours` (not queryable, set to 0 when complete)

Status 5=Complete zeros `remainingHours`.

### Resources

Entity: `Resources` (cannot delete)

**Key fields:** `id`, `firstName`, `lastName`, `email`, `userName`, `isActive`, `resourceType`, `licenseType` (read-only), `locationID` (read-only), `userType` (read-only), `hireDate` (read-only), `numberFormat`, `title`, `payrollIdentifier`, `internalCost` (read-only, returns 0 without permissions), `surveyResourceRating` (read-only)

### TimeEntries

Entity: `TimeEntries` (no UDFs)

**Key fields:** `id`, `resourceID`, `roleID`, `dateWorked`, `startDateTime`, `endDateTime`, `hoursWorked` (0-24), `hoursToBill` (read-only), `billingCodeID`, `contractID`, `ticketID`, `taskID`, `timeEntryType` (2=Ticket, 6=Task), `isNonBillable`, `summaryNotes` (required for tickets), `internalNotes`, `showOnInvoice`, `createDateTime` (read-only), `lastModifiedDateTime` (read-only)

### Contracts

Entity: `Contracts` (max 50 UDFs, cannot delete)

**ContractType values:**
| Value | Type |
|-------|------|
| 1 | Time & Materials |
| 2 | Fixed Price |
| 3 | Block Hours |
| 4 | Retainer |
| 5 | Incident |
| 7 | Recurring Service |

**Key fields:** `id`, `contractName`, `contractType`, `companyID`, `status`, `startDate`, `endDate`, `billingPreference`, `contactID`, `serviceLevelAgreementID`, `description`, `estimatedHours`, `estimatedCost`, `estimatedRevenue`, `exclusionContractID` (read-only), `isDefaultContract`, `isCompliant`

### Products

Entity: `Products` (max 100 UDFs, cannot delete)

**Key fields:** `id`, `name`, `isActive`, `isSerialized`, `productCategory`, `chargeBillingCodeID`, `unitCost`, `unitPrice`, `mSRP`, `billingType`, `periodType`, `priceCostMethod`, `description`, `manufacturerName`, `sKU`, `externalProductID`, `createdByResourceID` (read-only), `createdTime` (read-only)

### Inventory

Entities: `InventoryItems`, `InventoryLocations`, `InventoryProducts`, `InventoryStockedItems`, `InventoryStockedItemsAdd`, `InventoryStockedItemsRemove`, `InventoryStockedItemsTransfer`, `InventoryTransfers`, `InventoryItemSerialNumbers`, `PurchaseOrders`, `PurchaseOrderItems`, `PurchaseOrderItemReceiving`

**PurchaseOrder status values:**
| Value | Status |
|-------|--------|
| 1 | New |
| 2 | Submitted |
| 3 | ReceivedPartial |
| 4 | ReceivedFull |
| 5 | Cancelled |

**Serialized items:** Sum of onHandUnits + reservedUnits + transferredUnits + removedUnits + pickedUnits + deliveredUnits = 1.

**Non-serialized items:** Sum equals purchaseOrderItemReceiving.quantityPreviouslyReceived.

### Opportunities

Entity: `Opportunities` (max 200 UDFs, cannot delete)

**Key fields:** `id`, `title`, `companyID`, `ownerResourceID`, `status`, `amount`, `probability` (0-100), `projectedCloseDate`, `startDate` (read-only, creation date), `stage` (read-only), `closedDate`, `lostDate` (auto-set when status=Lost), `cost`, `description`, `lossReason`, `winReason`, `leadSource`, `rating`, `contactID`, `opportunityCategoryID`, `salesOrderID` (read-only)

### Quotes

Entity: `Quotes` (cannot delete)

**Key fields:** `id`, `name`, `opportunityID`, `effectiveDate`, `expirationDate`, `billToLocationID`, `shipToLocationID`, `soldToLocationID`, `companyID`, `contactID`, `quoteNumber` (read-only), `primaryQuote` (one per opportunity), `quoteTemplateID`, `paymentTerm`, `comment`

### Services

Entities: `Services`, `ServiceBundles`, `ServiceBundleServices`, `Subscriptions`, `SubscriptionPeriods` (query only), `ServiceCalls`, `ServiceCallTickets`, `ServiceCallTasks`, `ServiceLevelAgreementResults` (query only)

### BillingItems

Entity: `BillingItems` (mostly read-only, query/update only)

**BillingItemType values:**
| Value | Type |
|-------|------|
| 1 | Labor |
| 2 | ProjectCost |
| 3 | Cost |
| 4 | Expense |
| 5 | Subscription |
| 6 | RecurringService |
| 7 | RecurringServices |
| 8 | Milestone |

Only `webServiceDate` can be updated. Cost fields (`ourCost`, `extendedCost`) require permissions.

### Read-Only Entities

These entities support query only: `BillingCodes`, `BillingItemApprovalLevels`, `InvoiceTemplates`, `QuoteTemplates`, `InternalLocations`, `Modules`, `Version`, `ResourceRoles`, `ResourceTimeOffBalances`, `ResourceTimeOffApprovers`, `ServiceLevelAgreementResults`, `TicketHistory`, `DeletedTicketLogs`, `DeletedTicketActivityLogs`, `DeletedTaskActivityLogs`, `NotificationHistory`, `Surveys`, `SurveyResults`, `Skills`, `ShippingTypes`, `ClassificationIcons`, `SubscriptionPeriods`, `ContractServiceUnits`, `ContractServiceBundleUnits`

### Create-Only Entities

These entities support create only: `ContractServiceAdjustments`, `ContractServiceBundleAdjustments`, `InventoryStockedItemsAdd`, `InventoryStockedItemsRemove`, `InventoryStockedItemsTransfer`, `TimeOffRequestsApprove`, `TimeOffRequestsReject`, `BillingItemApprovalLevels`, `PurchaseOrderItemReceiving`

