## 10. ExecuteCommand (Deep Links)

### URL Format

```
https://ww[number].autotask.net/ExecuteCommand?Command={command}&Parameters={parameters}
```

### Available Commands

**Ticket commands:**
| Command | Parameters |
|---------|------------|
| `NewTicket` | Phone Number, Account ID, or GlobalTaskID |
| `OpenTicketDetail` | Ticket Number or Ticket ID |
| `OpenTicketTime` | TicketID; optionally TimeEntryID |
| `EditTimeEntry` | WorkEntryID |

**Account (Company) commands:**
| Command | Parameters |
|---------|------------|
| `NewAccount` | None |
| `OpenAccount` | Phone, AccountName, or Account ID |
| `EditAccount` | Phone, AccountName, or Account ID |
| `NewAccountNote` | Account ID |

**Contact commands:**
| Command | Parameters |
|---------|------------|
| `NewContact` | Phone, AccountName, or Account ID |
| `EditContact` | Email, FirstName, LastName, or Contact ID |
| `OpenContact` | Email, FirstName, LastName, or Contact ID |

**Opportunity commands:**
| Command | Parameters |
|---------|------------|
| `OpenOpportunity` | Opportunity ID |

**Asset commands:**
| Command | Parameters |
|---------|------------|
| `NewInstalledProduct` | Phone, Account ID, or AccountName |
| `EditInstalledProduct` | Asset ID |
| `OpenIPDW` | Wizard extension name |

**Other commands:**
| Command | Parameters |
|---------|------------|
| `OpenAppointment` | AppointmentID |
| `OpenContract` | ContractID |
| `OpenKBArticle` | Knowledgebase article ID |
| `OpenProject` | ProjectID |
| `OpenQuote` | Quote ID |
| `OpenSalesOrder` | SalesOrderID |
| `OpenServiceCall` | Service Call ID |
| `OpenTimeOffRequest` | ApproverID and ResourceID (required) |
| `OpenToDo` | ToDoID |

### Examples

```
https://ww3.autotask.net/ExecuteCommand?Command=OpenTicketDetail&Parameters=T20240115.0001
https://ww3.autotask.net/ExecuteCommand?Command=OpenTicketDetail&Parameters=12345
https://ww3.autotask.net/ExecuteCommand?Command=NewTicket&Parameters=11111
https://ww3.autotask.net/ExecuteCommand?Command=OpenAccount&Parameters=ACME%20Corp
https://ww3.autotask.net/ExecuteCommand?Command=OpenContact&Parameters=john@acme.com
https://ww3.autotask.net/ExecuteCommand?Command=EditTimeEntry&Parameters=67890
https://ww3.autotask.net/ExecuteCommand?Command=OpenProject&Parameters=54321
```

### Terminology Notes

| API Term | UI Term |
|----------|---------|
| Account | Company |
| Installed Product | Asset |

Parameters accept either terminology. URL-encode parameters (spaces and special characters).

